BuildTools:   ocamlbuild
Homepage:     https://github.com/pveber/bistro
OCamlVersion: >= 4.02
FilesAB:      etc/META.ab

PreInstallCommand:   $ocamlfind install ppx_bistro etc/META
PreUninstallCommand: $ocamlfind remove ppx_bistro

